{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-21", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "戰場靜悄悄", "storyInfo": "食腐者之王的部隊已經集結完畢，威靈頓公爵與深池部隊也已蓄勢待發。而九所帶領的新整合運動已經在亂局中找到了方向。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i13", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 30.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天空中的天災雲還未散去。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若你摘下手套，就能感受到空氣中的源石粉末刮過手掌的感覺。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食腐者之王坐在他的王座上，俯瞰著屬於他的大軍。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食腐者的軍隊不會動搖，食腐者的軍隊不會軟弱。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們穿過風暴，穿過傷痕，穿過敵人與同伴的屍骸。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲們仍在行軍，食腐者之王的敵人還沒有被徹底碾碎，他們便沒有資格停下。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們就是戰爭本身。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_244", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵閣下，我們的損失很重，先鋒部隊中有近三分之一的高速戰艦已經失去了行動能力，我們正在嘗試挽回局勢，但並不樂觀。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_244", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那場猛烈的天災......就這麼突兀地襲擊了我們的前沿陣線。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_244", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在如此高濃度的源石環境下，我們很難正常作戰，裸露的活性源石晶簇也極大限制了我方高速戰艦的機動性能。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_244", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是薩卡茲的軍隊並沒有受到太大影響，他們......完全不在乎。他們本來就幾乎都是感染者。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_244", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食腐者的軍隊中還出現了一些我們從未見過的巫術裝置。它們投擲出的那種混亂的裂隙......十分棘手，我們還在尋找反制措施。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維持陣線，讓後方的炮兵壓制戰場，讓開東邊的缺口。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#7$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_244", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白，馬上執行。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您對可憐的溫德米爾真是不留情面，威靈頓公爵。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她剛剛才救了我們派去爭搶玩具的那些艦隊，您這就恩將仇報，把薩卡茲趕向她的駐地？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有允許你接通我的通訊，開斯特。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您還是那麼死板。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會提醒溫德米爾做好準備，我們都還是維多利亞的一員。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老威靈頓，我清楚你想要什麼。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你太心急了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次，希望你用更符合身份的方式與我交換意見，開斯特。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#7$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威靈頓公爵閣下，您不該繼續站在甲板上了，這裡雖然離天災落下的地方有些距離，但這些粉塵一定不利於您的健康。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的職責，愛布拉娜殿下。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您總是那麼值得信賴。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵......那對兄妹很謹慎。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎片大廈的威力絕不僅限於此，他們不想讓我們知道，他們究竟是還沒完全掌握風暴的力量，還是......在等待一個更好的機會。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是本該屬於維多利亞的風暴，如今，我們卻率先面對了它。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽見軍官們在緊張地低語，公爵閣下，但您看起來並不慌亂。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您甚至還有些......興奮？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，愛布拉娜殿下，我不否認。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片戰場讓人畏懼，讓人尊敬。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自高盧的老近衛軍之後，我已經多久沒有遇上過這樣的對手了？", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們早就做好了準備。無論掌握在誰的手中，風暴只會為塔拉人洗去猶疑與軟弱，而我們年輕的部隊，將從中淬煉而出。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能看見他......那位食腐者之王。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#3$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們放下所有的矯飾，面對彼此的軍陣吧。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉人不會在這裡停下，我們的憤怒也不比你們的要少。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜殿下，我會為您，為塔拉人贏得下一個時代。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忠誠的公爵......", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會有一個結論的，很快。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_victoria", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎你，埃芒加德女士，你帶來了屬於巫妖的善意。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不會忘記，在這個薩卡茲急需團結的時刻，巫妖選擇了走出你們的圖書館，選擇了站在我們的身邊。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼呼，別說得那麼正式，特蕾西婭殿下，我只是一位觀察員而已。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你還是送來了禮物，前線的將士們會妥善使用它的。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是些擺弄裂隙的小伎倆罷了。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫妖們所掌握的有關空間的知識，確實超脫了我們絕大部分人的認知。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，不像一直在卡茲戴爾的你們，我們巫妖都是些惜命的傢伙，找個安全的地方藏“命結”才是頭等大事。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但王庭的議事廳中，從未撤去過屬於巫妖的那把椅子。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......感謝您的惦念，殿下。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#3$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您應該知道，在我來的路上，那位凱爾希勳爵拜訪過我。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她十分努力地想要說服我......不要站在你們這一邊。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喪鐘的王庭那位年輕的主人正與他們並肩而戰，我聽老師們提起過，那位女妖的強大不容忽視。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希勳爵聲稱，您與攝政王掀起的這場戰爭，只是在把這片大地推向更加無可挽回的失序與紛爭。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些都只是暫時的，我們......必須忍受。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "團結所需的共識，只能如此建立。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您知道最有趣的是什麼嗎，殿下？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您和那位勳爵的說辭真的很像。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都在呼籲著團結。你們都告訴我，在即將到來的災難之前，這是唯一的出路。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#3$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......凱爾希。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那為什麼，你們會站在彼此的對立面呢？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許只是......我們都很心急。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放心，我作為巫妖王庭的信使，沒有給凱爾希勳爵任何承諾。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像也沒有給你們任何承諾一樣。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們巫妖向來不急著給自己選一個立場。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些漫長的痛苦與破碎的心......它們終究會有一個歸宿。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......阿米婭，你能找到那條路嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_056"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 5.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_ep12", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g10_wildbattlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些該死的軍官！在他們眼裡，帶上隻牙獸都比帶上我們更有意義！", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他以為他是什麼？要是放在以前，我還沒得病的時候，他都不敢抬起頭看我！", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，該死，這*維多利亞粗口*的礦石病！", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我寧願那幫自稱羅德島的人沒給我打抑制劑，我寧願自己在諾伯特區炸成一攤源石粉塵。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最起碼還能撒那些看熱鬧的混蛋一臉！還能讓他們也體驗體驗我的感覺！", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈！那個卡特斯還給我留了一份抑制劑......", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些藥*維多利亞粗口*的根本救不了我！", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我完了。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走不出這裡了。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的生活......一切都完了。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從諾伯特區裡爬了出來又有什麼用？這該死的源石，我身體裡這些該死的源石！", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刺穿我！乾脆點，刺穿我！", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感染者市民憤怒地抓撓著手臂上的源石結晶，彷彿只要捏碎它們，一切就仍然可以恢復如初。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇痛襲來，這位新晉感染者大口呼吸著，他被這種剛剛開始熟悉起來的痛苦掀翻在地，淚水混著汗水從他的臉頰滾落。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他仰面躺在一片泥濘之中，視野裡，是正在升向高點的太陽。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在閉上眼前，一縷粉色的髮絲闖入了他的視線。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡可不是個曬日光浴的好地方，先生。這些泥把你的衣服都弄髒啦。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "躲開我，我是個感染者，搞不好下個小時就爆炸了。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，我猜你得礦石病絕對沒有超過一個星期，頭幾天裡，每個人都和你的樣子差不多。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "震驚和否認，痛苦和內疚，憤怒和消沉......", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後只能接受自己確實是個可憐蟲和倒楣蛋。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你懂什麼？你——", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是個感染者，有什麼好奇怪？", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是個感染者？你看起來明明是這麼地......", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，我見過你......", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，先生，我叫珀茜瓦爾，是日落街酒店的門童。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來您沒什麼行李要我幫您提的，真遺憾。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不，不是在諾伯特區......", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哦？那真是稀奇。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當了很多年騎警，珀茜瓦爾小姐，我經手過一些案子，其中有些也與感染者有關。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，我真該反思下以前對待他們的態度，現在，我也成了他們的一員啦。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道一個組織，他們的行蹤甚至觸及了倫蒂尼姆周邊。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得他們叫......", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珀茜瓦爾，你在這裡做什麼呢？", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，雷德。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在路邊撿到了一個感染者，應該是被溫德米爾公爵的人扔在這裡的。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是一個？", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，珀茜瓦爾，要不是你在諾伯特區與倫蒂尼姆的分離程式剛剛啟動的時候就發出了消息，這些感染者的下場，可能會淒慘得多。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼哼，我向來以我的敏銳自豪。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#2$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也虧你想得出來，居然把和我們的通訊偽裝成倫蒂尼姆的公開廣播發出來。你該感謝我有個聽收音機的好習慣。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒你想像的那麼容易，我可是把酒店裡的通訊站拆了，好不容易才找到個地方傳遞消息的。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是把羅德島和那位戴菲恩小姐害慘了。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們到底是......", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽說過“整合運動”嗎？", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#9$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整合運動？！你們——", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，你們都來了。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹得好，珀茜瓦爾。這一路我們接收了很多感染者，他們的情況比我們一開始預想的要好得多。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在地塊裡，主要是雷德在幫助他們啦，我大部分時間倒是都在偷懶。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然不想承認，羅德島確實也有一份功勞。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......羅德島，他們果然也在這裡。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......整合運動，我知道你們的事蹟。", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次，你們想給維多利亞帶來什麼災難？", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，先生，你搞錯了。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是那些從昔日整合運動的廢墟上收集殘骸的人。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們已經與曾經不同。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不會捨棄這個名字和其中的罪孽，錯誤必須被銘記，但我們也必須展開新的行動，重新在感染者之中證明自己。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的整合運動不再需要一個領袖，我們走過各個國家，我們和那些認同我們的感染者團體們並肩而戰。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們到底想要做什麼？", "name": "感染者市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藥物和同情無法真正地幫助感染者，但是團結與力量可以。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感染者沒有祖國，先生，那麼，新的整合運動就是他們的立足之處。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有興趣加入我們嗎？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g10_wildbattlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉，你在看什麼？", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#5$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......還未散去的天災雲，碎片大廈啟動了。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，又會多出多少感染者。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還有一個消息要帶給你，塔露拉。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見到了一個......使用紫色火焰的德拉克。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是嗎。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珀茜瓦爾，這些日子，我時常在想——", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，的確存在一種人，他們天生擅長掀起浪潮。他們會聲稱這一切總是由他們推動，由他們引領，由他們創造。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某種意義上，他們往往能成功......但我永遠都不會稱他們為勝利者。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會承認......他們所締造的這一切，值得被稱為“歷史”。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我永遠不會承認。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}